01:08:35,528 --> 01:08:38,823
一年以后，我们从地下出来
So, a year later, we started coming out,

556
01:08:39,365 --> 01:08:40,575
人们徘徊着
and people wandered around.

557
01:08:40,658 --> 01:08:46,539
我不知道要做什么，只想找个地方活下来
I, not knowing what I was gonna do,trying to find a place to survive.

558
01:08:47,832 --> 01:08:50,543
一天，我听到了一个声音
One day, I heard a voice.

559
01:08:51,878 --> 01:08:54,797
很难解释，但它听起来像…
It's hard to explain, but it was like it...

560
01:08:55,131 --> 01:08:57,759
好像从我内心深处发出来的
Like it was coming from inside of me.

561
01:08:58,634 --> 01:09:02,889
但我可以听到它，就好像我听到你跟我说话这样清楚
But I could hear it as clear as I can hear you talking to me now.

562
01:09:03,431 --> 01:09:05,391
那个声音说了什么？
What did this voice say?

563
01:09:05,933 --> 01:09:07,268
它指引我
It led me

564
01:09:08,186 --> 01:09:10,730
去一个地方，我找到了这本书
to a place where I found the book

565
01:09:11,105 --> 01:09:13,274
埋在一些碎石下面
buried under some rubble.

566
01:09:17,236 --> 01:09:21,032
那个声音告诉我把这本书带到西方
The voice told me to carry the book out west.

567
01:09:22,492 --> 01:09:26,162
告诉我有条路会指引我
Told me that a path would be laid out for me,

568
01:09:26,245 --> 01:09:30,833
我会被带到一个使这本书会安全的地方
that I'd be led to a place where the book was safe.

569
01:09:34,545 --> 01:09:36,756
它告诉我，会有人保佑我
Told me that I'd be protected

570
01:09:38,132 --> 01:09:41,344
任何人或事都阻碍不了我前进
against anyone or anything that stood in my path.

571
01:09:44,514 --> 01:09:46,933
我从那时起就一直在走
I've been walking ever since.

572
01:09:48,434 --> 01:09:52,271
你这么做的原因就是因为你听到的一个声音告诉你的？
And you did all that because a voice in your head told you to?

573
01:09:53,106 --> 01:09:54,440
是的
Yes, I did.

574
01:09:55,274 --> 01:09:57,068
我清楚当时我听到了什么
I know what I heard.

575
01:09:57,485 --> 01:09:59,237
我也清楚现在我所听到的
I know what I hear.

576
01:09:59,737 --> 01:10:01,572
我知道我没疯
I know I'm not crazy.

577
01:10:02,281 --> 01:10:05,451
我知道没有他的保佑，我永远不会成功
And I know I would've never made it without help.

578
01:10:06,786 --> 01:10:09,330
- 那是什么？- 太多问题了
- What's that?- One question too many.

579
01:10:09,789 --> 01:10:12,917
睡觉吧，我们早上要很早上路
Go to bed, we got an early start in the morning.

580
01:10:50,580 --> 01:10:51,664
嘿
Hey.

581
01:11:03,718 --> 01:11:04,802
嘿

582
01:11:10,433 --> 01:11:12,518
凯马特- 你好，我叫艾利

583
01:11:15,188 --> 01:11:16,939
你在做什么？
What are you doing?

584
01:11:17,315 --> 01:11:19,817
- 抱歉，我以为你在睡觉- 我没睡
- I'm sorry, I thought you were sleeping.- I wasn't sleeping.

585
01:11:19,901 --> 01:11:21,652
你在做什么？
What are you doing?

586
01:11:22,278 --> 01:11:23,821
我只是想看看那本书
I just wanted to see the book.

587
01:11:23,905 --> 01:11:26,866
除了我谁也不能碰它，你明白吗？
Nobody touches it but me, you understand me?

588
01:11:27,533 --> 01:11:29,076
你听明白了吗？
Do you understand me?

589
01:11:29,160 --> 01:11:31,871
- 是的，我明白- 好的，去睡觉
- Yes, I understand.- Good. Go to sleep.

590
01:11:41,839 --> 01:11:44,759
你说过你不认识字，它对你没有用
You said you don't know how to read anyway. It's no use to you.

591
01:11:44,842 --> 01:11:45,927
是的
Yeah.

592
01:11:46,969 --> 01:11:48,387
那教我读
So teach me.

593
01:12:08,616 --> 01:12:10,785
等等！停！
Hold up. Hold up! Stop!

594
01:12:16,624 --> 01:12:18,960
你说你已经走了30年了，是吗？
You know, you say you've been walking for 30 years, right?

595
01:12:19,043 --> 01:12:20,253
是的
Right.

596
01:12:20,795 --> 01:12:22,380
你想过你可能迷路了吗？
Have you ever thought that maybe you were lost?

597
01:12:22,463 --> 01:12:23,589
没有
Nope.

598
01:12:23,923 --> 01:12:26,008
你怎么知道你走的方向是正确的？
Well, how do you know that you're walking in the right direction?

599
01:12:26,092 --> 01:12:28,553
“我们行事为人，是凭着信心不是凭着眼见”
"We walk by faith, not by sight."

600
01:12:29,595 --> 01:12:30,805
那是什么意思？
What does that mean?

601
01:12:30,888 --> 01:12:34,517
意思是你知道它是正确的，尽管还没有被证明
It means that you know something,even if you don't know something.

602
01:12:34,600 --> 01:12:35,685
这完全说不通
That doesn't make any sense.

603
01:12:35,768 --> 01:12:37,728
没必要说得通，这是信仰，是信仰
Doesn't have to make sense,it's faith. It's faith.

604
01:12:37,812 --> 01:12:40,815
在一片漆黑里，这是光亮的花朵
It's the flower of light in the field of darkness

605
01:12:40,898 --> 01:12:43,359
给了我前进的力量，你明白吗？
that's giving me the strength to carry on. You understand?

606
01:12:43,442 --> 01:12:44,694
这是书里的？
Is that from your book?

607
01:12:44,777 --> 01:12:48,739
不，是强尼卡什在福尔松监狱的演唱
No, it's Johnny Cash live at Folsom Prison.

608
01:12:49,448 --> 01:12:50,533
什么？
What?

609
01:13:13,347 --> 01:13:16,517
- 你认为有人住在那里吗？- 不知道
- Do you think anyone lives there?- I don't know.

610
01:13:18,227 --> 01:13:19,979
也许那儿有水
Maybe there's water.

611
01:13:29,864 --> 01:13:31,407
待在我后面
Stay behind me.

612
01:13:31,866 --> 01:13:36,495
禁止擅自闯入

613
01:13:36,621 --> 01:13:38,122
这有点奇怪
This is weird.

614
01:14:13,324 --> 01:14:14,700
你们是谁？
Who are you?

615
01:14:18,454 --> 01:14:21,207
我们只是过路的，不是坏人
We're travelers, that's
all. Don't mean any harm.

616
01:14:21,290 --> 01:14:24,126
禁止擅自闯入！你没看到标志吗？
No trespassing! Haven't you read the sign?

617
01:14:25,044 --> 01:14:27,463
对不起，我没看到
We're very sorry. I didn't see it.

618
01:14:27,922 --> 01:14:29,131
你在这儿干什么？
What's your business?

619
01:14:29,215 --> 01:14:30,299
- 是…
- 没事！
- We were just...
- No business!

620
01:14:30,383 --> 01:14:34,804
只是，我们非常抱歉，如果你们允许，我们这就离开
Just... We're very sorry, and if you let us, we'll be on our way.

621
01:14:35,513 --> 01:14:38,891
乔治，看他们，其中一个只是个小姑娘
George, look at them. One of them is just a girl.

622
01:14:38,974 --> 01:14:42,895
是的，老生常谈，我已经听过无数遍了
Yeah. It's an old story, I've heard it a hundred times before.

623
01:14:43,020 --> 01:14:47,400
我们最近很少有访客来，乔治有点疑神疑鬼
We get so few visitors these days.George is suspicious of everybody.

624
01:14:47,733 --> 01:14:51,404
我是玛莎，你们想喝点茶吗？
I'm Martha. Would you care for some tea?

625
01:15:02,164 --> 01:15:05,042
来点音乐如何？旋律很放松
How about some music? It's so soothing.

626
01:15:05,751 --> 01:15:06,961
乔治！
George!

627
01:15:26,939 --> 01:15:30,443
你觉得怎么样？很好听，请喝
How do you like it? It's nice. Please.

628
01:15:41,078 --> 01:15:45,124
- 好喝吗？- 很好，味道很浓郁
- Is that good?- Good, good. That's... Taste is rich.

629
01:15:49,962 --> 01:15:53,549
你们两个能互相依赖活到现在，真了不起
It's amazing that you two have survived out here all by yourselves.

630
01:15:53,632 --> 01:15:56,886
乔治是一个能工巧匠
Well, now, George is something of a handyman.

631
01:15:59,305 --> 01:16:02,558
他为这个地方干了很多活，使这里更安全
He did a lot of work on
this place, making it safe.

632
01:16:02,767 --> 01:16:05,269
我们也许老了，但我们适应性很强
We may be old, but we're resilient.

633
01:16:05,936 --> 01:16:08,939
我们遇到很多人，想从我们这儿抢走这个地方
We've known more than a few who've tried to take this place from us.

634
01:16:09,023 --> 01:16:11,192
- 没错吧，乔治？- 是的，我们遇到过
- Haven't we, George?- Yes, we have.

635
01:16:11,275 --> 01:16:13,903
- 是的- 我给你们看点东西，过来
- Right.- I wanna show you something. Come on.

636
01:16:13,986 --> 01:16:16,238
乔治，别！现在不行！
George, no! Not now!

637
01:16:17,239 --> 01:16:18,491
过来！
Come on!

638
01:16:21,243 --> 01:16:23,370
- 这些是…- 坟墓？当然
- Are these...- Graves? Sure.

639
01:16:23,662 --> 01:16:25,831
不埋葬他们很不文明
Be uncivilized not to bury them.

640
01:16:25,915 --> 01:16:28,334
另外，这对土地有好处
Besides, it's good for the soil.

641
01:16:29,293 --> 01:16:32,797
快进来，我想我可能会给你们做点三明治
Come on back inside. I think I might be able to rustle you up some sandwiches.

642
01:16:32,880 --> 01:16:35,174
谢谢，非常感谢
Well, thank you, thank you very much.

643
01:16:35,257 --> 01:16:36,801
- 得走了- 他们把这些人都杀了
- We gotta go now.- They killed all these people.

644
01:16:36,884 --> 01:16:38,469
不只杀了他们，还吃了他们
They didn't just kill them, they ate them.

645
01:16:38,552 --> 01:16:41,472
- 她的手，她的手在抖- 太多人肉了，我们走
- Her hands... Her hands were shaking.- Too much human meat. Let's go.

646
01:16:42,139 --> 01:16:44,850
我找到了些肉，我想你们饿了
I found some meat. I hope you're hungry.

647
01:16:45,017 --> 01:16:46,560
没有，谢谢
Nope. No, thank you.

648
01:16:46,644 --> 01:16:49,438
我们得走了
Well, we... We gotta be going.

649
01:16:49,522 --> 01:16:51,732
- 这么快？- 是的，很抱歉
- So soon?- Yeah, I'm afraid so.

650
01:16:51,816 --> 01:16:54,443
- 你确定你不留下？- 我肯定，非常肯定
- Are you sure you won't stay?- I'm sure, I'm very sure.

651
01:16:54,527 --> 01:16:56,320
把枪放下
Put the gun down.

652
01:16:56,487 --> 01:16:58,280
索拉娜，你拿着这个，把门打开
Solara, you take this. Open the door for us, please.

653
01:16:58,364 --> 01:17:00,491
- 索拉娜，说感谢你的茶- 感谢你的茶
- Solara, say thank you for the tea.- Thank you for the tea.

654
01:17:00,574 --> 01:17:01,784
非常感谢你的茶
Thank you so much for the tea.

655
01:17:09,625 --> 01:17:11,293
回到里面去
Go back inside.

656
01:17:15,256 --> 01:17:16,298
乔治，怎么了？
George, what's wrong?

657
01:17:16,382 --> 01:17:18,801
一群武装的强盗
Whole company of armed degenerates, that's what's wrong!

658
01:17:18,884 --> 01:17:20,427
他们把他们引到这里
And they led them straight to us.

659
01:17:20,761 --> 01:17:23,848
- 我刚摆好瓷器- 去他妈的瓷器！
- I just set out the good china.- Fuck the china!

660
01:17:23,931 --> 01:17:25,141
你还有其他武器吗？
Have you got any more weapons?

661
01:17:25,224 --> 01:17:27,935
武器？给你看看我的武器
Weapons? I'll show you some weapons.

662
01:17:31,355 --> 01:17:33,691
- 你会开枪吗？- 当然
- Can you shoot a gun?- Of course.

663
01:17:35,025 --> 01:17:36,861
快！快！
Come on, come on!

664
01:17:37,069 --> 01:17:39,155
我们知道你们在里面！
We know you're in there!

665
01:17:40,239 --> 01:17:42,867
出来没人会受伤！
Come on out and nobody needs to get hurt!

666
01:17:47,621 --> 01:17:49,498
我会放你一马！
I'll make it easy!

667
01:17:49,790 --> 01:17:52,585
把索拉娜和书交出来！
Send out Solara with the book!

668
01:17:53,002 --> 01:17:55,588
- 我们怎么办？- 我知道我他妈的在干什么！
- What are we gonna do?- I know what the fuck I'm doing!

669
01:17:55,671 --> 01:18:00,467
- 等等- 我只想要这两样，书和姑娘！
- Wait, wait, wait.- That's all I want, the book and the girl!

670
01:18:02,261 --> 01:18:04,138
他们不会出来
They ain't coming out.

671
01:18:29,914 --> 01:18:33,626
该死！趴下！大家趴下！
Shit! Get down! Everybody, get down!

672
01:18:52,227 --> 01:18:54,772
嘿！你听到的那个声音
Hey! You know that voice you heard?

673
01:18:54,980 --> 01:18:56,815
它有没有告诉你这件事？
Did it say anything about this?

674
01:18:56,899 --> 01:18:59,318
我们会活着出去的，我们俩个！
We'll get out alive, both of us!

675
01:18:59,485 --> 01:19:00,986
那我们呢？
What about us?

676
01:19:01,779 --> 01:19:03,530
没提到你们！
Didn't mention you!

677
01:19:12,581 --> 01:19:13,958
停止开火！
Cease fire!

678
01:19:14,833 --> 01:19:16,210
停止开火！

679
01:19:26,887 --> 01:19:28,889
玛莎？玛莎？
Martha? Martha?

680
01:19:28,973 --> 01:19:32,017
玛莎！玛莎！
Martha! Martha!

681
01:19:35,229 --> 01:19:38,274
- 玛莎- 到边上去！到那边！
- Martha.- Go in on the side! Over on the side!

682
01:19:38,357 --> 01:19:39,817
你们这帮混蛋！
You bastards!

683
01:19:40,567 --> 01:19:43,612
- 在房子的侧面！- 你们他妈的这帮混蛋！
- The side of the house!- You fucking bastards!

684
01:19:48,951 --> 01:19:52,371
- 别开枪！别开枪！- 他们在干什么？
- Hold your fire! Hold your fire!- What are they doing?

685
01:19:52,454 --> 01:19:54,123
没有好事
Nothing good.

686
01:21:08,072 --> 01:21:09,698
书在哪儿？
Where's the book?

687
01:21:16,622 --> 01:21:18,165
看看他的包
Check his pack.

688
01:21:36,809 --> 01:21:38,310
不在这儿
It ain't here.

689
01:21:41,105 --> 01:21:45,943
这是你最后的机会，不交出书，我就把你埋在这儿
This is your last chance. You give it up or I swear I'll bury you out here.

690
01:21:56,829 --> 01:21:58,330
狗娘养的
Son of a bitch.

691
01:21:58,664 --> 01:22:00,457
我们再试试
Let's try this again.

692
01:22:05,170 --> 01:22:07,131
- 卡内基！
- 什么？
- Carnegie!
- What?

693
01:22:17,307 --> 01:22:20,811
书在哪儿？
Now, where's the book?

694
01:22:26,024 --> 01:22:28,068
把书给他吧，拜托
Give him the book, please.

695
01:22:32,906 --> 01:22:34,533
别告诉他
Don't tell him.

696
01:22:43,542 --> 01:22:46,795
在房子里，电视机后面
It's in the house, back of the TV.

697
01:22:49,006 --> 01:22:50,591
检查电视机！
Go check the TV!

698
01:22:51,216 --> 01:22:52,509
什么？
The what?

699
01:22:52,968 --> 01:22:56,680
你他妈的在开什么玩笑！你，去！
You're fucking shitting me. You, go! Go!

700
01:23:33,050 --> 01:23:36,261
无论求什么，只要信，就必得着
Ask, and you shall receive.

701
01:23:41,767 --> 01:23:43,644
上帝是好人，是吗？
God is good, is he not?

702
01:23:45,187 --> 01:23:46,647
一直是
All the time.

703
01:23:49,024 --> 01:23:50,651
不是一直
Not all the time.

704
01:24:17,010 --> 01:24:18,929
不！不！
No! No!

705
01:25:04,516 --> 01:25:05,767
你现在明白了？
You see?

706
01:25:08,020 --> 01:25:09,688
我怎么告诉你的？
What did I tell you?

707
01:25:15,694 --> 01:25:17,321
他只是个人
He's just a man.

708
01:25:21,199 --> 01:25:23,827
不！把他放了！
No! Leave him alone!

709
01:25:24,536 --> 01:25:26,121
求求你，住手！
Please, stop!

710
01:25:32,711 --> 01:25:34,838
你的保护神在哪？
Where's your protection now?

711
01:25:49,895 --> 01:25:51,313
为我祈祷
Pray for me.

712
01:25:54,816 --> 01:25:55,901
可以吗？
Okay?

713
01:26:00,655 --> 01:26:02,032
我认真的
I mean it.

714
01:27:20,235 --> 01:27:21,319
不！
No!

715
01:27:29,202 --> 01:27:30,495
狗屎！
Shit!

716
01:27:31,997 --> 01:27:33,415
回去！
Go back!

717
01:28:17,209 --> 01:28:19,044
快！快！
Come on! Come on!

718
01:29:18,603 --> 01:29:22,691
我们剩的油刚刚可以回去，你想去追她吗？
We barely got enough fuel to make it back. You wanna go after her?

719
01:29:24,109 --> 01:29:25,151
不
No.

720
01:30:46,399 --> 01:30:50,904
- 你要往哪儿走？- 我要去西边，必须去西边
- Where are you going?- I'm going west. Gotta go west.

721
01:30:53,615 --> 01:30:54,699
嘿！
Hey!

722
01:31:01,915 --> 01:31:03,041
来
Here.

723
01:31:20,225 --> 01:31:21,559
对不起
I'm sorry.

724
01:31:22,102 --> 01:31:23,561
对不起什么？
For what?

725
01:31:24,187 --> 01:31:26,481
- 这，这都是我的错- 不，不是的
- This. This is all my fault.- No, it's not.

726
01:31:26,564 --> 01:31:30,819
不，是我的错，如果我不跟着你这些就不会发生了
No, it is. If I didn't come with you, none of this would've happened.

727
01:31:31,653 --> 01:31:33,405
这不是你的错
It's not your fault.

728
01:31:36,074 --> 01:31:37,826
我做了必须要做的事
I did what I had to do.

729
01:31:37,909 --> 01:31:41,371
我认为任何事情都不能使你放弃那本书
I didn't think anything could make you give up that book.

730
01:31:41,454 --> 01:31:43,915
我以为它太重要了
I thought it was too important.

731
01:31:46,501 --> 01:31:50,588
这么多年，我背着它，每天阅读
All the years I've been carrying it and reading it every day.

732
01:31:52,424 --> 01:31:55,343
我只痴迷于想保护它
I got so caught up with keeping it safe,

733
01:31:55,427 --> 01:31:59,723
我忘了靠从中学到的去生活
I forgot to live by what I learned from it.

734
01:32:00,849 --> 01:32:02,767
是的，那是什么？
Yeah, and what's that?

735
01:32:03,768 --> 01:32:04,936
只是…
Just...

736
01:32:08,273 --> 01:32:11,401
帮助他人要多于帮助自己
Do for others more than you do for yourself.

737
01:32:13,695 --> 01:32:16,322
这是我从中学到的
That's what I got from it, anyway.

738
01:33:02,911 --> 01:33:04,454
你闻到了吗？
You smell that?

739
01:33:05,497 --> 01:33:07,332
- 什么？- 空气中的味道？
- What?- In the air?

740
01:33:07,457 --> 01:33:08,666
盐？
Salt?

741
01:33:13,379 --> 01:33:15,882
我们靠近大海了
We're getting close to the ocean.

742
01:34:14,899 --> 01:34:16,234
到了
That's it.

743
01:34:18,444 --> 01:34:19,779
到了

744
01:34:52,854 --> 01:34:54,480
把机械师叫来！
Get the Engineer!

745
01:36:26,572 --> 01:36:28,241
别再靠近！
That's far enough!

746
01:36:29,534 --> 01:36:31,619
你们在这里干什么？
What's your business here?

747
01:36:33,121 --> 01:36:34,664
我叫艾利
My name is Eli!

748
01:36:35,540 --> 01:36:38,418
我有一本英王詹姆士版的圣经
I have a King James Bible in my possession.

749
01:36:38,501 --> 01:36:40,003
待在那里！
Remain where you are!

750
01:36:40,086 --> 01:36:44,173
别试图有什么动作，否则就开枪！
Don't attempt to make any sudden moves, or you will be fired upon!

751
01:37:01,065 --> 01:37:04,444
小心！小心！
Be careful with it. Be careful.

752
01:37:11,242 --> 01:37:12,869
小心
Careful with it.

753
01:37:22,962 --> 01:37:24,464
他们没有武器
They're clean.

754
01:37:25,757 --> 01:37:28,593
我们做这件事已经很久了
We've been doing this for a long time now.

755
01:37:30,762 --> 01:37:34,098
- 感觉像一座博物馆- 不是，比博物馆更好
- Feels like a museum.- No, it's much more than that.

756
01:37:34,557 --> 01:37:37,352
这里是我们重新开始的地方
This is where we're going to start again.

757
01:37:38,061 --> 01:37:41,856
我们有一个印刷机，它很快就可以工作了
We've got a printing press.It'll be operational quite soon.

758
01:37:41,939 --> 01:37:45,360
我们准备教导人们
让他们了解那个失去的世界
We're going to teach people about the world they lost.

759
01:37:45,443 --> 01:37:47,653
帮助他们重建
Help them start to rebuild it.

760
01:37:47,737 --> 01:37:52,158
我是指，你看，莎士比亚大百科全书，只少了几卷
I mean, look. Shakespeare. Britannica,missing only a few volumes.

761
01:37:52,408 --> 01:37:56,162
这是一整套莫扎特和瓦格纳的唱片
There's a whole series of beautiful Mozart and Wagner records

762
01:37:56,245 --> 01:37:58,498
还保存得很好
in still very pristine condition.

763
01:37:58,581 --> 01:38:01,292
但就是没有圣经，不过现在有了
But never a Bible. Well, not until now.

764
01:38:02,210 --> 01:38:05,129
我能问一下它是什么状况？
Well, may I ask what condition it's in?

765
01:38:06,839 --> 01:38:08,299
它很破旧了
It's beat up,

766
01:38:09,258 --> 01:38:11,135
但还能用
but it will do the job.

767
01:38:11,969 --> 01:38:14,889
- 我可以看一下吗？- 是的，可以
- Do you think I could see it?- Yes, you may.

768
01:38:22,730 --> 01:38:25,149
- 好了，打开了- 你打开了吗？
- That's it. It's open.- You there?

769
01:38:59,767 --> 01:39:01,310
你有什么要写的吗？
Do you have anything to write on?

770
01:39:01,394 --> 01:39:04,355
可以给我们一些纸吗？
Could you get us some writing paper, please?

771
01:39:05,022 --> 01:39:06,607
很多纸
And a lot of it.

772
01:39:08,151 --> 01:39:09,819
很多很多
A whole lot of it.

773
01:39:10,862 --> 01:39:12,238
难以置信
It can't be.

774
01:39:13,865 --> 01:39:14,866
这…
It...

775
01:39:19,996 --> 01:39:21,581
这不可能！
It's impossible!

776
01:39:23,291 --> 01:39:24,709
这不可能！
It can't be!

777
01:39:27,879 --> 01:39:31,382
仔细点，记下
Pay close attention and write down

778
01:39:33,176 --> 01:39:34,886
我说的每一句话
everything I say

779
01:39:36,220 --> 01:39:39,015
我说的每个字
exactly as I say it.

780
01:39:43,686 --> 01:39:45,771
“摩西的第一卷书
"The first book of Moses.

781
01:39:48,900 --> 01:39:50,526
“叫《创世记》
"Called Genesis.

782
01:39:51,277 --> 01:39:54,447
“第一章，第一节
"Chapter one, verse one.

783
01:39:58,367 --> 01:40:00,119
“起初
"In the beginning,

784
01:40:01,412 --> 01:40:03,372
“上帝创造天
"God created the heavens

785
01:40:05,499 --> 01:40:07,084
“地
"and the earth.

786
01:40:11,005 --> 01:40:12,340
“第二节
"Verse two.

787
01:40:14,759 --> 01:40:18,721
“地是空虚
"And the earth was without form

788
01:40:21,849 --> 01:40:23,184
“混沌
"and void.

789
01:40:28,022 --> 01:40:29,565
“渊面
"And darkness

790
01:40:31,734 --> 01:40:34,654
“黑暗
"was upon the face of the deep.

791
01:40:38,324 --> 01:40:40,409
“上帝的灵
"And the Spirit of God

792
01:40:42,453 --> 01:40:43,913
“运行
"was hovering

793
01:40:46,791 --> 01:40:49,001
“在水面上
"over the face of the waters.

794
01:40:52,838 --> 01:40:54,257
“第三节
"Verse three.

795
01:40:57,969 --> 01:40:59,470
“上帝说
"And God said,

796
01:41:03,724 --> 01:41:05,601
“要有光
"'Let there be light.'

797
01:41:10,773 --> 01:41:12,650
“就有了光”
"And there was light."

798
01:41:23,369 --> 01:41:24,996
索拉娜在哪？
Where is Solara?

799
01:41:28,708 --> 01:41:30,042
在外面
Out there.

800
01:41:31,168 --> 01:41:32,503
她自己选的
Her choice.

801
01:41:33,629 --> 01:41:37,425
我试图把她带回来，她拒绝了
I tried to bring her back. She refused.

802
01:41:41,679 --> 01:41:44,098
她拒绝后你做了什么？
What did you do when she refused?

803
01:41:50,479 --> 01:41:52,606
- 读- 你对我女儿做了什么？- Read it.
- What did you do to my daughter?

804
01:41:52,690 --> 01:41:55,901
- 读！- 你对我女儿做了什么？- Read it!
- What did you do to my daughter?

805
01:42:14,045 --> 01:42:16,088
你准备好就可以开始了
You can start anytime.

806
01:42:24,597 --> 01:42:25,931
对不起
I'm sorry.

807
01:42:28,684 --> 01:42:31,228
太久了，我不记得了
It's been so long, I don't remember.

808
01:42:38,736 --> 01:42:41,572
- 你必须记得- 必须？是吗？
- You have to.- I have to? Really?

809
01:42:41,697 --> 01:42:44,241
不，你必须记得，拜托
No, no, no, no. You have to. Please.

810
01:42:47,912 --> 01:42:49,163
你的腿
Your leg.

811
01:42:50,539 --> 01:42:52,500
它已经不疼了
It doesn't hurt anymore.

812
01:42:54,251 --> 01:42:55,753
我能闻到
I can smell it.

813
01:43:10,601 --> 01:43:13,020
你为了那本书这么努力
You worked so hard for that book.

814
01:43:14,522 --> 01:43:17,274
你牺牲了这么多人
You sacrificed so much, so many men.

815
01:43:19,735 --> 01:43:21,779
现在连保护你的人都没了
More than you could spare.

816
01:43:23,781 --> 01:43:27,785
以前那些怕你的人，连你的名字都不敢说
Now all those people who were too scared to even say your name,

817
01:43:27,952 --> 01:43:32,123
他们现在就在楼下，正在破坏酒吧呢，你知道吗？
they're downstairs, tearing up the bar right now. Did you know that?

818
01:43:32,706 --> 01:43:35,334
没有人去阻止他们
And there's no one there to stop them.

819
01:43:36,669 --> 01:43:38,462
而你却病了
And you're feverish.

820
01:43:41,549 --> 01:43:44,885
我想象不出那种感受，梦寐以求的书就在眼前
I can't imagine what it must feel like to have what you want so close

821
01:43:44,969 --> 01:43:48,639
- 而你却无从解读它- 闭嘴！
- and it might as well be a million miles away.- Stop it!

822
01:43:52,184 --> 01:43:53,936
你要离开我吗？
Are you leaving me?

823
01:43:56,647 --> 01:43:57,857
克劳迪娅？
Claudia?

824
01:44:00,317 --> 01:44:01,694
克劳迪娅？

825
01:44:05,156 --> 01:44:06,532
克劳迪娅！
Claudia!

826
01:44:33,642 --> 01:44:35,144
走开！
Get away! Get away!

827
01:44:35,227 --> 01:44:36,228
这是我的！
It's mine!

828
01:45:55,349 --> 01:45:56,767
亲爱的主
Dear Lord,

829
01:45:57,393 --> 01:45:59,937
感谢你赐我力量和信念
thank you for giving me the strength and the conviction

830
01:46:00,020 --> 01:46:02,815
去完成你交付给我的任务
to complete the task you entrusted to me.

831
01:46:23,294 --> 01:46:26,589
《创世记》

832
01:46:27,381 --> 01:46:33,387
感谢你在充满荆棘的道路上持续、真诚地指引我
Thank you for guiding me, straight and true, through the many obstacles in my path,

833
01:46:37,725 --> 01:46:39,059
艾利

834
01:46:39,143 --> 01:46:42,688
使我在周围都迷失的情况下，仍然保持坚毅
and for keeping me resolute when all around seemed lost.

835
01:46:43,606 --> 01:46:47,818
感谢你的保护和这一路上的指引
Thank you for your protection and for your many signs along the way.

836
01:46:49,320 --> 01:46:53,908
感谢那些你使我做过的好事，我对我做的坏事感到抱歉
Thank you for any good that I may have done. I'm so sorry about the bad.

837
01:46:55,951 --> 01:46:59,246
你知道你不需要离开，欢迎你留下
You don't have to leave, you know.You're very welcome to stay here.

838
01:46:59,330 --> 01:47:02,458
- 你会非常安全的- 谢谢
- You'll be perfectly safe.- Thank you,

839
01:47:03,751 --> 01:47:06,503
但有些事我必须要做
but this is something that I have to do.

840
01:47:11,175 --> 01:47:12,843
你要去哪？
Where will you go?

841
01:47:14,136 --> 01:47:15,220
家
Home.

842
01:47:21,393 --> 01:47:23,729
感谢你让我结交的朋友
Thank you for the friend I made.

843
01:47:23,938 --> 01:47:27,107
请像照看我那样照看她
Please watch over her as you've watched over me.

844
01:47:48,337 --> 01:47:51,382
感谢你最后允许我安息
Thank you for finally allowing me to rest.

845
01:47:51,882 --> 01:47:53,801
我真的非常累
I'm so very tired,

846
01:47:54,510 --> 01:47:57,262
但是我现在平静地安息
but I go now to my rest, at peace,

847
01:47:58,347 --> 01:48:02,017
因为知道我在这地球上活着的时候所做的是正确的
knowing that I have done right with my time on this earth.

848
01:48:02,601 --> 01:48:07,856
圣经 - 新英王詹姆士译本 阿尔卡特拉斯印刷

849
01:48:11,026 --> 01:48:12,987
那美好的仗我已经打过了
I fought the good fight.

850
01:48:13,821 --> 01:48:15,572
当跑的路我已经跑尽了
I finished the race.

851
01:48:19,034 --> 01:48:20,661
所信的道我已经守住了
I kept the faith.


